# Pricing
https://cloud.google.com/run/pricing

https://cloud.google.com/vpc/network-pricing#internet_egress

Cloud Run (fully managed) charges you only for the resources you use, rounded up to the nearest 100 millisecond.

Free Tier:

2 vCPU days per month

4 GiB day per month

1 GiB egress within North America



Tier 2

30c per GiB day

$2.90 per vCPU day

Egress: https://cloud.google.com/vpc/network-pricing#internet_egress

Australia: $0.19/GB
Rest of the world: $0.12/GB

Unless a container instance must be kept idle due to the minimum number of container instances configuration setting, it will not be kept idle for longer than 15 minutes.

